    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "Py68s5RlrxTASYCT7b11twieRZCiSTEQ8jmDsGWoqpI=",
    "originContent": "Xpano is a tool for panorama stitching with focus on simplicity and ease of use, major features include:",
    "translatedContent": "Xpanoは、シンプルさと使いやすさに焦点を当てたパノラマ合成ツールで、主な機能は以下の通りです："
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "ebVZ6eNur9BR4GgoDrueT09V6kySyJnDueYD3QHKsbo=",
    "originContent": "- Auto detection of groups of images that can be stitched into panoramas",
    "translatedContent": "- パノラマに合成可能な画像グループの自動検出"
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "k71/71dKaEH307zGMYvYiGTsRUjvQUKCIOdkzyc+b74=",
    "originContent": "- Preview + zoom + pan of the computed panoramas",
    "translatedContent": "- 計算されたパノラマのプレビュー＋ズーム＋パン"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "ZSrQl2k74foXpLJSxrPfOwa5T0j9xUMXWIE2qHjyDlY=",
    "originContent": "- Crop mode, boundary auto fill, selectable projection types",
    "translatedContent": "- トリミングモード、境界の自動塗りつぶし、選択可能な投影タイプ"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "IE2mqkSQlgSFIFESLTReDghnGpsLpW2SwfrLPITwX34=",
    "originContent": "- Projection adjustments: pitch, yaw and roll",
    "translatedContent": "- 投影調整：ピッチ、ヨー、ロール"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "XCsRhoIEsDBp2jDqGMbBES1gJBCAaUS49PMpYt4X2bM=",
    "originContent": "- Export of full resolution panoramas including exif metadata",
    "translatedContent": "- EXIFメタデータを含むフル解像度パノラマのエクスポート"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
